{"type":"step-attempt","step":"design","sessionId":"41d653f5-e055-4fd7-9cd8-3f12f1bbf551","outcome":{"verdict":"success","findingsPath":null,"error":null,"toolResult":{"ok":true,"reason":"Wrote design.md, spec.md, tasks.md under specrunner/changes/round-immutable-input/ on branch change/round-immutable-input-b794df81. Plan covers: (D1) relocate resume-input one-shot ownership from StepExecutor to Pipeline.runInternal, removing the in-place deps mutation; (D2) ParallelReviewRound builds a readonly per-round execution input; (D3) preserve automatic resume context across member→coordinator mapping via mapMemberToCoordinator; (D4) fix intended distribution invariants (human note → all pending members, automatic context → target member) without fixing the accidental behavior. architecture/ untouched (B-16 ratify deferred). No src/ or README edits performed — planning only.","status":"success"},"followUpAttempts":1,"transientRetryAttempts":0},"startedAt":"2026-07-13T18:55:53.889Z","endedAt":"2026-07-13T19:08:17.832Z"}
